==English==

===Etymology===
Widely believed to be short for non-educated[sic] delinquent although this is in fact a [[backronym]] and folk etymology.

===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# (''British (especially Scottish) derogatory slang'') A person, usually a youth, of low social standing and education, a violent disposition and with a particular style of dress (typically sportswear or burberry), speech and behaviour.

